Radius Gold Inc.


            
            Radius Gold, Inc. is a natural resource property exploration company. The company engages in acquisition and exploration of mineral properties. It holds interest in Tlacolula Silver Project, Holly-Banderas Project, and Margarita Silver Property. The company was founded by Simon T. P. Ridgway on July 1, 2004 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


