 Find Your Home




Northern California



From snow-capped mountains to sunny beaches, Northern California offers a great quality of life for Pulte homebuyers. Pulte communities here are located near big cities and small towns offering residents a range of shopping, dining and cultural experiences. With plenty of quality finishes to choose from and spacious, flexible layouts, you’ll be sure to find the perfect place to call home in Northern California.












